    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>序幕是一个有限的游戏版本，旨在让您熟悉完整的游戏。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人或最多 4 人合作游戏。将您的单人游戏会话开放给其他玩家和朋友一起玩。您也可以从大厅加入游戏，通过语音和文字聊天与他人一起供应快餐。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/5b354349b23c90df9742849f2d404b16.poster.avif?t=1734375277\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/5b354349b23c90df9742849f2d404b16.webm?t=1734375277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/5b354349b23c90df9742849f2d404b16.mp4?t=1734375277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >处理快餐店顺利运营所需的一切。体验真实的饮料机、烤架和油炸锅的操作。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/5ba833081b342a7624f4832f0b989ee9.poster.avif?t=1734375277\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/5ba833081b342a7624f4832f0b989ee9.webm?t=1734375277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/5ba833081b342a7624f4832f0b989ee9.mp4?t=1734375277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索快餐店的混乱本质，这里随时都可能发生意想不到的离奇事件，挑战你和你的餐厅工作人员通过团队合作来应对。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/81164ff959849c8bb695e3af06a9689c.poster.avif?t=1734375277\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/81164ff959849c8bb695e3af06a9689c.webm?t=1734375277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/81164ff959849c8bb695e3af06a9689c.mp4?t=1734375277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >明智地管理自己的时间至关重要，因为你要分清任务的轻重缓急，让客户满意，让生产线顺利运转。团队协调是关键，因此要有效委派任务，确保无缝操作。准备好迎接快节奏的快餐世界吧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/f4d6d07475d5054f17ad75656155b59b.poster.avif?t=1734375277\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/f4d6d07475d5054f17ad75656155b59b.webm?t=1734375277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099020/extras/f4d6d07475d5054f17ad75656155b59b.mp4?t=1734375277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快餐模拟器序章》包括</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 单人游戏和可选的 1-4 人合作游戏 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 煎炸和烹饪 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 文本和语音聊天 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 饮料和冰淇淋机 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 等级上限为 15</p></li></ul>",
